Tap and Pay System
│
├── 1. User Module
│   ├── Registration & Login
│   ├── Wallet / Bank Account Linking
│   └── Transaction History & Profile Management
│
├── 2. Payment Module
│   ├── Tap-to-Pay Processing
│   ├── Payment Authentication & Security
│   ├── Payment Confirmation Notification
│   └── Error Handling & Alerts
│
├── 3. Conductor Module
│   ├── Payment Verification
│   ├── Boarding Assistance Tools
│   └── Transaction Status Dashboard
│
├── 4. Admin / Backend Module
│   ├── System Monitoring
│   ├── Report Generation
│   ├── Revenue & Transaction Management
│   └── User & Device Management
│
├── 5. Integration Module
│   ├── Payment Gateway Integration
│   ├── Bank APIs
│   └── NFC Reader Device Integration
│
└── 6. Maintenance & Security Module
    ├── System Updates & Patches
    ├── Data Security & Encryption
    └── Logging & Audit Trails
